CatDescriptText: The ice cream flavors are listed for October and include butter crunch, strawberry, chocolate, black raspberry, buttered hazelnut, chocolate chip, vanilla, coffee, and peach.  Sign on back wall reads "Credit extended to those over 80 years and accompanied by their parents."
TitMainTitle: Woman behind counter of ice cream store advertising Sealtest ice cream, Quirky beverage, Nut Meats, and Bud's Pretzels
